text: The Wicked League () is a 2015 Hong Kong sitcom series produced by Hong Kong Television Network. The first episode premiered on 22 June 2015. ==Cast== * David Chiang * Yuen Wah * Kwok Fung * Pai Piao * Peter Lai * Lee Fung * Fung So-bor * May Tse * Cheng Shu-fung * Wong Ching * Bonnie Wong * Crystal Leung * Rachel Lam ==Release== A 6-minute preview was released on HKTV's YouTube channel on 16 June 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Official website Category:Hong Kong Television Network original programming Category:2015 Hong Kong television series debuts Category:2010s Hong Kong television series
